plan:

jira filter ID --- opens all issues that match the filter on that ID
jira issue ID --- opens the issue that match the given ID
jira search "jql" --- performs a search with the given jql syntax
jira start ID --- assigns the current user to the user and sets the issue on 'On Progress'
jira resolve STATUS MSG --- closses the issue with the given status and message
jira issues STATUSSES --- opens all issues that are assigned to the current user and matches the given statusses
jira new PROJECT SUMMARY
    - DESCRIPTION
    --- Creates a new issue for the PROJECT and asks the user to give (optional) a description

next step:

let users define which columsn they want


